briefTitle: A Study to Compare SB17 (Proposed Ustekinumab Biosimilar) to Stelara® in Subject With Moderate to Severe Plaque Psoriasis
officialTitle: A Phase III, Randomised, Double-blind, Multicentre Clinical Study to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Immunogenicity of SB17 (Proposed Ustekinumab Biosimilar) Compared to Stelara® in Subjects With Moderate to Severe Plaque Psoriasis
summary: This is a randomised, double-blind, multicentre clinical study to evaluate the efficacy, safety, tolerability, PK, and immunogenicity of SB17 compared to Stelara® in subjects with moderate to severe plaque psoriasis.

primaryOutcome.measure: Percent Change From Baseline in PASI at Week 12
